== Overview ==
A battery of four [[Baron Laser|Baron Lasers]] linked into a single slot coupling. The resulting projectile from this weapon has the power of four baron lasers all in one shot.

== Where to Acquire ==
The Baron Battery can be bought in the workshop or found in caves, vaults, and bot remains in Vulcore.
